---
// DMCA Policy
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 8, 2026';
---

<Layout 
  title="DMCA Policy - GuildPost"
  description="GuildPost DMCA Policy and copyright infringement reporting procedures. Learn how to submit takedown notices."
  url="https://guildpost.tech/dmca"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen" style="background-color: var(--bg-primary);">
    <Header />
    
    <main class="pt-20 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">DMCA Policy ⚖️</h1>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0]">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-[#8892b0] max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-[#8892b0] mb-8">
            GuildPost respects the intellectual property rights of others and expects users of our platform to do the same. This DMCA Policy outlines our procedures for handling copyright infringement claims.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA)</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            The Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) provides a mechanism for copyright owners to request the removal of infringing material from online service providers. GuildPost complies with the DMCA and responds promptly to valid takedown notices.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Reporting Copyright Infringement</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            If you believe that content on GuildPost infringes your copyright, please send a written DMCA takedown notice containing the following information:
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-6 mb-3">Required Information:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Physical or electronic signature</strong> of the copyright owner or authorized agent</li>
            <li><strong>Identification of the copyrighted work</strong> claimed to be infringed (or a representative list if multiple works)</li>
            <li><strong>Identification of the infringing material</strong> and its location on our platform (URL or specific location)</li>
            <li><strong>Your contact information</strong> (address, telephone number, email)</li>
            <li><strong>Good faith statement</strong> that you believe the use is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law</li>
            <li><strong>Accuracy statement</strong> under penalty of perjury that the information in the notice is accurate and that you are authorized to act on behalf of the copyright owner</li>
          </ol>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Where to Send Notices</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Send DMCA takedown notices to our designated agent:
          </p>
          <div class="p-4 bg-[#12121a] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-lg mb-4">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">GuildPost DMCA Agent</p>
            <p class="text-[#8892b0]">Email: <a href="mailto:dmca@guildpost.tech" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">dmca@guildpost.tech</a></p>
            <p class="text-[#8892b0] mt-2">Please include "DMCA Takedown Notice" in the subject line.</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Counter-Notification</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            If you believe your content was removed in error or misidentification, you may submit a counter-notification containing:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Your physical or electronic signature</li>
            <li>Identification of the removed content and its location before removal</li>
            <li>Statement under penalty of perjury that you have a good faith belief the content was removed by mistake</li>
            <li>Your contact information and consent to jurisdiction of the federal court in your district</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Send counter-notifications to the same email address above with "DMCA Counter-Notification" in the subject line.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Repeat Infringers</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            GuildPost will terminate the accounts of users who are determined to be repeat infringers. A repeat infringer is a user who has been notified of infringing activity more than twice or has had content removed for infringement more than twice.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Processing Timeline</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            We strive to process all DMCA notices within:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Acknowledgment:</strong> Within 24 hours of receipt</li>
            <li><strong>Initial review:</strong> Within 2 business days</li>
            <li><strong>Content removal (if valid):</strong> Within 3 business days of receipt</li>
            <li><strong>Counter-notification processing:</strong> Within 10-14 business days</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. False Claims</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            Please note that under Section 512(f) of the DMCA, any person who knowingly materially misrepresents that material or activity is infringing may be subject to liability for damages. Ensure your claims are accurate and made in good faith.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">8. Trademark Infringement</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            For trademark infringement claims (not copyright), please email <a href="mailto:legal@guildpost.tech" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">legal@guildpost.tech</a> with details of the infringement and your contact information.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8892b0] mb-4">
            For questions about our DMCA policy, contact us at:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#8892b0] mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>DMCA Notices: <a href="mailto:dmca@guildpost.tech" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">dmca@guildpost.tech</a></li>
            <li>Legal Inquiries: <a href="mailto:legal@guildpost.tech" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">legal@guildpost.tech</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[#2a2a3a]">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/terms" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">Terms of Service</a>
            <span class="text-[#2a2a3a]">|</span>
            <a href="/privacy" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
            <span class="text-[#2a2a3a]">|</span>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-[#00f5d4] hover:underline">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
